# Import / export

- API: `web/src/app/api/storeAdmin/[storeId]/RESOURCE/export/route.ts` and `import/route.ts`.
- Access: `CheckStoreAdminApiAccess(storeId)`.
- Export: POST → JSON via `transformPrismaDataForJson`; sensible filename + timestamp.
- Import: validate JSON shape (Zod); upsert in transaction; log with logger.
- UI: buttons on `client-resource.tsx` + `import-resource-dialog.tsx`.

Copy an existing resource (e.g. tables/facilities) when adding a new exportable entity.
